relation: A Starman that I made look sort of shiny by fooling around with a series of Photoshop filters.
That purple-haired chick from the EB64 screenshots.
Messing around with filters again, I liked the effect I got here -- almost like newspaper print.
Someday. Someday I'll be able to do a really good version of the Carbon Dog. Until then, this is what we've got.
